tip.text: Try their slice fish soup delicious nice 😃👍🍲☕️🍴😊
The Homemade spinach skin bean curd is a must try 😍🍺🎉🍝㊗️😊
An average coffee shop but should try the satay beehoon the grouper soup the wanton mee & their signature chilli crab 😊🍺🍝🍲🍜🍦🍻
